'''伊利沙伯二世登基鑽禧紀念'''（{{lang-en|Diamond Jubilee of Queen Elizabeth II}}）是2012年的一項多國慶祝活動，以紀念60年前[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]在1952年2月6日繼承駕崩的父親[[乔治六世|乔治六世]]，登基成為[[英国|英国]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]、[[新西兰|新西兰]]、[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]、[[南非|南非]]、錫蘭（現名[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]）女王；登基鑽禧紀念時伊利沙伯二世為16個[[英聯邦王國|英聯邦王國]]女王。除她以外，英國歷史和[[英联邦|英联邦]]歷史上只曾有[[维多利亚_(英国女王)|維多利亞女王]]在1897年慶祝登基鑽禧周年紀念<ref name=PA>{{Cite news| title=Extra bank holiday to mark Jubilee| publisher=Press Association| date=2010-01-05| url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ukpress/article/ALeqM5iFc6Cmk-AJ72Mo5lMkmGuUqHSxIw| accessdate=2010-01-05| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mYhY2Lxk?url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ukpress/article/ALeqM5iFc6Cmk-AJ72Mo5lMkmGuUqHSxIw| archivedate=2010-01-05| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=DCHportrait>{{cite web| url=http://www.pch.gc.ca/pc-ch/infoCntr/cdm-mc/index-eng.cfm?action=doc&DocIDCd=CJM100694| last=Department of Canadian Heritage| title=Government of Canada Commissions New Canadian Portrait of Her Majesty The Queen| publisher=Queen's Printer for Canada| date=2010-06-22| accessdate=2010-06-23| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610171934/http://www.pch.gc.ca/pc-ch/infoCntr/cdm-mc/index-eng.cfm?action=doc&DocIDCd=CJM100694| archive-date=2011-06-10| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.pm.gc.ca/eng/media.asp?category=1&featureId=6&pageId=26&id=3927| last=Office of the Prime Minister of Canada| title=PM unveils Diamond Jubilee Medal design to honour Canadian contributions| date=2011-02-09| publisher=Queen's Printer for Canada| accessdate=2011-10-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111115003737/http://www.pm.gc.ca/eng/media.asp?category=1&featureId=6&pageId=26&id=3927| archive-date=2011-11-15| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.pch.gc.ca/eng/1296669421850/1296669769856| last=Department of Canadian Heritage| title=Topics > Monarchy in Canada > Queen's Diamond Jubilee| publisher=Queen's Printer for Canada| accessdate=2011-10-20| archive-date=2011-09-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110905012335/http://www.pch.gc.ca/eng/1296669421850/1296669769856| dead-url=no}}</ref>。按照傳統，多個以伊利沙伯二世為元首的國家都會頒授鑽禧獎章<ref name=PA /><ref name=GG>{{cite web| url=http://www.gg.ca/pdf/DiamondJubilee_eng.pdf| last=Office of the Governor General of Canada| title=Queen Elizabeth II Diamond Jubilee Medal| publisher=Queen's Printer for Canada| accessdate=2011-02-03| archive-date=2011-08-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806041434/http://gg.ca/pdf/DiamondJubilee_eng.pdf| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 概覽 ==
{{Quote box| width=250px| border=1px| align=right| bgcolor=#F5F5DC| quote=
今天慶祝作為你們的女王60年。很感謝這些年來，你們對我和菲利普親王的支持和鼓勵，藉此告訴你當收到有關登基鑽禧紀念的消息時如何深受感動。
在這個特別的年頭，希望大家再一次體會到患難與共的力量、以及家庭、友誼、以至是鄰里互助所匯聚的能量。在位多年以來與家人巡訪英國和英聯邦各地，有幸從所見所聞中看到不少生動的例子。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.royal.gov.uk/LatestNewsandDiary/Pressreleases/2012/TheQueensDiamondJubileemessage.aspx| last=Royal Household| title=The Queen's Diamond Jubilee message| date=2012-02-06| publisher=Queen's Printer| accessdate=2012-02-08| archive-date=2014-11-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141128215921/http://www.royal.gov.uk/LatestNewsandDiary/Pressreleases/2012/TheQueensDiamondJubileemessage.aspx| dead-url=yes}}</ref>| salign=right| source=伊利沙伯二世（2012年）}}
